<h2><strong>Dream Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اني-حامل?page=1033" > I am pregnant </a> for a pregnant woman</strong></h2>
<p>Ibn Sirin sees that seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> in a dream is a sign that she is suffering from many psychological pressures in her life and cannot deal with them, and she also thinks about <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الحمل-والولادة-لابن-سيرين?page=1" > pregnancy and childbirth </a> all the time and feels excessive pressure.  Pregnancy in the dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> is an indication that her lifestyle is changing dramatically after childbirth.</p>
<p>As for those who saw that they were pregnant with a male in her dream, it is better that she gives birth to a male, and the same interpretation applies to the woman's pregnancy in a dream, this also indicates that she will give birth.  Giving birth to a female.</p>
<p>If <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> sees in her dream that she is pregnant and gave birth to children in reality, this is also a good omen for abundant sustenance and good that will occur in the dreamer's life.  And Ibn Shaheen had a different opinion when interpreting this dream, as he mentioned that the dreamer's husband will take an important position and benefit his life together with great benefit.  .</p>
<h2><strong>Dream Interpretation: I am pregnant from a divorced woman</strong></h2>
<p>Interpreting the vision of I am pregnant in a dream for a divorced woman is an indicator of an urgent desire to forget the past and start a new and better beginning towards her future, as the dream symbolizes that she will be able to get rid of all the problems and fits that she has been suffering from for a long time.  Ibn Sirin believes that pregnancy in the dream of a divorced woman is a sign of an opportunity to return to her ex-husband, and their lives together will improve greatly.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
